Description: RMA of Texas provides high quality care in regard to fertility, providing the latest technology in regard to IVF, IUI, ICSI and more.

As part of the RMA network, our patients have access to our Select Comprehensive Chromosome Screening (Select CCS) which is the only validated form of pre-implantation genetic screening shown to be both safe and an efficacious method to increase the chances of successfully conceiving and having a healthy baby. Your situation is unique. That’s why RMA takes the time to get to know you so we can offer a personalized approach to your diagnosis and treatment. We provide a wide array of treatment options including IVF (In-Vitro Fertilization), IUI (Intra-Uterine Insemination), and ICSI (Intra-Cytoplasmic Sperm Injection) that are tailored to the individual by our Reproductive Endocrinologists. So what are you waiting for? Experience how RMA of Texas can help you achieve your dream of starting a family today.

Its creators want to simplify collaboration by placing documents within the web browser and equipping users with wiki-like editing functionality and, more importantly, an email-like messaging system that associates messages with particular documents. Lunarr works like this: to begin collaborating on a document, you can either upload a file to Lunarr or give it a URL (for online docs hosted at places like [Google](/organization/google) or [Zoho](/organization/zoho)). Or you can start from scratch with a template. Then you can hit the tab located in the upper-right hand corner of the screen to â€œflipâ€ the page over. On the â€œother sideâ€ exists a messaging tool that lets you send a message to others using their email addresses, whether or not they are Lunarr users. These messages can not only be used to discuss the document in question, but also to bestow access to the document to others.

Organization Name: Precise Water Damage Restoration of Portland
Description: If you require water damage restoration in Portland OR, look no further! Precise Water Damage Restoration of Portland is the solution.
Full Description: At Precise Water Damage Restoration of Portland, we understand the devastating impact water damage can have on your home or commercial property. From burst pipes to flooding, water damage can cause extensive structural damage and even pose health risks to occupants. That's why our team of experts is dedicated to delivering exceptional results to each client. Our highly motivated individuals are passionate about their work and committed to assisting homeowners and commercial property owners with their water damage issues. As a result, our Portland water damage restoration services have earned us a reputation of excellence, as evidenced by the 5-star ratings we have received. If you want to experience the best in Portland water damage restoration services, reach out to us today! Here are some expert tips and advice on how to deal with water damage in your property: Act fast and call the professionals The longer you wait to address water damage, the more extensive and costly the repairs will be. As soon as you notice any signs of water damage, such as damp or moldy walls, ceilings, or floors, call our team of experts at Precise Water Damage Restoration of Portland. We have the experience, knowledge, and equipment to assess the damage, extract the water, and restore your property to its pre-loss condition. Turn off the power and gas supply Before our team arrives, it's important to turn off the power and gas supply to your property. This will prevent any electrical or gas hazards and ensure the safety of everyone involved. Document the damage Before any restoration work begins, it's important to document the extent of the damage. Take photos and videos of the affected areas, and make a list of all damaged items. This will help with your insurance claim and ensure that all repairs are covered. Dry out the affected areas Once our team has extracted the water, we will use industrial-strength fans and dehumidifiers to dry out the affected areas. This will prevent mold growth and further damage to your property. Address any mold issues If mold is present in your property, it's important to address it immediately. Mold can cause health issues and spread quickly if left untreated. Our team has the expertise to safely remove mold and prevent it from returning. Consider preventative measures To prevent water damage from occurring in the future, consider taking preventative measures such as installing a sump pump, sealing basement walls, and regularly maintaining your plumbing and appliances. At Precise Water Damage Restoration of Portland, we're committed to providing our clients with the best possible service and results. Contact us today to learn more about our Portland water damage restoration services and how we can help you with your water damage issues.

Description: Reclaimed Building Material Consultant
Full Description: PlanetReuse (PR) was founded on a simple, but revolutionary idea: make reclaimed building material reuse easier and more people will do it.    PlanetReuse is a reclaimed materials consultancy and brokerage firm.  PR expertly matches reclaimed materials with designers, builders, and owners to save projects money, serve LEED (Leadership in Energy and Environmental Design) efforts and sustain the planet.  PR grew over 300% last year.  Having encouraged and coordinated the reuse of building materials for hundreds of commercial jobs, our work has made us a national leader in commercial green building.   After spending the last four years building a reclaimed building materials network to serve the commercial building industry, PlanetReuse is now launching an effort to bring this monumental opportunity to every day citizens across the U.S.  Our aim is to make reclaimed building materials top-of-mind and easy-to-access so both commercial and residential building owners who need materials for a construction project, consider 'used' materials before 'new.’  And when it’s time for demolition or renovation we want reuse to be THE obvious alternative to the landfill. To increase awareness of, and access to, reused/surplus residential building materials, we will soon introduce PlanetReuse Marketplace (PRM).  PRM will be a national, social media-enabled website that allows customers to locate, view, share and eventually buy inventory from the roughly 1,100 for-profit and non-profit reuse centers in the U.S.  (e.g. Habitat for Humanity ReStore, Chicago's Rebuilding Exchange) that sell used and surplus materials at 40-60% off the price of new.  Reuse centers will populate the site with their inventories via our proprietary technology, InvenQuery, which uses a mobile phone application to instantly -- and in a single work-flow -- post new inventory online upon intake and remove it at point-of-sale.    The InvenQuery technology platform, which incorporates e-commerce and social media marketing, has been designed in collaboration with reuse centers nationwide and will fundamentally change the trajectory of reclaimed building material sales.  The reuse center industry is growing 15-20% per year, yet straw polls suggest only 2 of 10 Americans are even aware of reuse centers.   Furthermore, they sell less than 5% of inventory online, using a clunky manual posting process for Craigslist or Facebook.  PRM, powered by InvenQuery will change this.  We will bring connection, convenience, awareness and credibility to the reuse industry, ultimately making it as easy to shop online for reclaimed building materials as it is to shop for new materials from Home Depot or Lowe’s.
Industry Groups: Commerce and Shopping, Real Estate, Sustainability
